The '''Aldabra Island day gecko''', or '''Aldabra day gecko''' ('''''Phelsuma abbotti abbotti'''''), has been found on the [[Aldabra Atoll]] ([[Seychelles]]).  It lives on low trees and bushes and eats [[insect]]s and fruit.

